Introduction My talk is about extracting seeds from hardware wallets. I am chief security officer at Ledger. I joined Ledger a bit more than one year ago. I built the Ledger Donjon which is an independent red team. Our mission is to help secure Ledger&rsquo;s products. So what we do day to do is try to break all the hardware wallets. We continuously challenge the security of our products.
